divs: Sighting DetailsI was reviewing the photos of my last trip to San Francisco and noticed that a flying object appeared at the left of the City Hall dome. I had taken other photos (one 8 secs before and another 40 secs later) in the same position and the UFO doesn't appear in them. I took these photos using a SONY model DSC-W90.
